snippet.title: Siege Physics - Alpha Demo Trailer
snippet.description:
Try the demo on itch.io: https://trickshotlabs.itch.io/siege-physics-demo

Siege Physics is a sandbox puzzle game set in the middle ages. Use the available resources to build siege engines capable of transporting the ragdoll foot solider to his goal. Or just crush him with stone balls

Music: The Land of Luck by Spectacular Sound Productions
